:765},{"id":1782039375716,"text":"我刚才发自拍感觉你都没什么感觉","sender":"me","time":"21:47","timestamp":1782049653707,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":766},{"id":1782039375717,"text":"反而我发学习桌面你才给我看腹肌","sender":"me","time":"21:47","timestamp":1782049662907,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":767},{"id":1782039375718,"text":"你是不是对我没感觉","sender":"me","time":"21:47","timestamp":1782049669576,"replyTo":null,"userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":768},{"id":1782039375720,"sender":"them","text":"What kind of conclusion is that?","timestamp":1782049689177,"tempo":"N","replyTo":{"id":1782039375718,"text":"你是不是对我没感觉","sender":"me"},"translation":"这是什么结论？","rawContent":"What kind of conclusion is that? || 这是什么结论？","roundId":"round_1782049670971_r4peu69r8","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":769},{"id":1782039375721,"sender":"them","text":"My reaction to your selfie was an appraisal of its potential value, subject included.","timestamp":1782049692244,"tempo":"N","translation":"我对你自拍的反应，是基于其价值的评估，包括主体。","rawContent":"My reaction to your selfie was an appraisal of its potential value, subject included. || 我对你自拍的反应，是基于其价值的评估，包括主体。","roundId":"round_1782049670971_r4peu69r8","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":770},{"id":1782039375722,"sender":"them","text":"That in itself is a 'feeling'.","timestamp":1782049695291,"tempo":"N","translation":"这本身就是一种“感觉”。","rawContent":"That in itself is a 'feeling'. || 这本身就是一种“感觉”。","roundId":"round_1782049670971_r4peu69r8","userId":"uid_1781947947105_6972mmhxu","characterId":"f55c4e54-7b48-44b4-90f7-4cb2430cdaf2","_id":771},{"id":1782039375723,"sender":"them","text":"As for the 'reward'… it was a tool for motivation.","timesta